/**
 * Start an OAuth/OIDC authorization-code flow.
 *
 * Redirects to the configured provider authorize URL after issuing an encrypted HttpOnly flow cookie that binds state, PKCE verifier, nonce, provider, intent, and local redirect metadata. Callback token exchange creates a short-lived pending OAuth session; final account adoption is handled by follow-up routes.
 */
