/**
 * Inspect a pending OAuth/OIDC decision session.
 *
 * Reads the short-lived HttpOnly `srapi_oauth_pending` cookie and returns a safe profile summary plus the next console action. This endpoint is read-only and does not consume the pending session token.
 */
