/**
 * Bind a pending OAuth/OIDC identity to the current console user.
 *
 * Uses the short-lived HttpOnly `srapi_oauth_pending` cookie plus the current console session and CSRF header to attach the verified external identity to the authenticated user. The pending session is consumed only after a successful bind, and the response never exposes raw upstream subjects, provider-subject hashes, authorization codes, provider tokens, session cookies, or CSRF tokens. An optional body may opt in to adopting the provider display name onto the account profile.
 */
